  <math|v<rsub|k>=<sqrt|<frac|1|2\<omega\><rsub|k>>>e<rsup|-i\<omega\><rsub|k>\<tau\>>>.

  <subsection|The solution for <math|k>-mode>

  Now let's consider the solution of eqn(<reference|kmodeeqn>) in the epoch
  of inflation:

  For the slow-roll condition, we have <math|\<omega\><rsub|k><rsup|2>=k<rsup|2>-<frac|z<rsub|S><rprime|''>|z<rsub|S>>\<simeq\>k<rsup|2>-<frac|1|\<tau\><rsup|2>><around*|(|\<nu\><rsub|S><rsup|2>-<frac|1|4>|)>>,
