  <math|z<rsub|S>=<wide|z|~><rsub|S><around*|(|<frac|-\<tau\>|-<wide|\<tau\>|~>>|)><rsup|-\<nu\><rsub|S>+<frac|1|2>>=<wide|z|~><rsub|S><around*|(|-<wide|\<tau\>|~>|)><rsup|\<nu\><rsub|S>-<frac|1|2>><around*|(|<frac|x|k>|)><rsup|<frac|1|2>-\<nu\><rsub|S>>>,
  where <math|<wide|\<tau\>|~>> is some arbitary time which will get a good
