  <\equation>
    \<cal-R\><rsub|k><around*|(|\<tau\>|)>=<frac|i|<sqrt|2>><frac|1|<wide|z|~><rsub|S>><around*|(|-<wide|\<tau\>|~>|)><rsup|<frac|1|2>-\<nu\><rsub|S>>k<rsup|-\<nu\><rsub|S>>\<propto\>k<rsup|-\<nu\><rsub|S>>
